<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>MyTutor Signup Code</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; }
    .code { background: #e5e7eb; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>MyTutor</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Your Signup Code</h2>
      <p>Hello!</p>
      <p>You requested a signup code for your MyTutor account. Here's your 4-digit code:</p>
      
      <div class="code">
        <%= @code %>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Important:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>This code will expire in 10 minutes</li>
        <li>If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email</li>
        <li>Never share this code with anyone</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The MyTutor Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 